game.name: Anna Fashion Shopping
game.description:
Hello ladies! The beautiful Anna is on a mission to shop for her all desirable things and she has chosen you to help her make a decision on every purchase. Do you think that you are skilled enough to guide her for the most successful shopping? Join Anna Fashion Shopping and get ready to enjoy your day shopping with Anna! This beautiful princess relies on your shopping and fashion abilities a lot, so do not make her feel down and help her buy the product that suites her lovely personality. 

You will get an opportunity to explore different shopping stores, including boutique shop, fancy jewelry store, shoes store and style fashion dresses store. Enter every store one by one to buy all the trendy outfits, shoes and other needful accessories for the girl in this one of the best girls games! Once your shopping is complete, make sure to take her to the salon where you have to give her a new hairstyle. It will depend upon your choice which store you want to go first.

In style fashion store, you will find lovely top and legging, trendy frocks and crop and top. In boutique shop, there will be an exciting range of handbags and purses are waiting for her. In shoes store, you can help her to pick up a pair of matching shoes. The fancy jewelry store will open up some good options of matching ornaments used to enhance your look. Do not forget to take her to the salon where you can choose a fabulous hairstyle for the princess in this shopping game. Good luck to check out more princess dress up games for kids and have a blast without download!
